Package main

Class Journey

java.lang.Object
main.dataStructure
main.Journey
public class Journey
extends dataStructure
The methods used in the interface concerning the journey aspect of things are kept here.

This class forms a journey, and the variables are easily accessed with "dataStructure.journeys.get(journeyID)" which returns a journey object.
